<br>
Is this bad? Comments please<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/bteamskald.showUserPublicProfile?gid=clapperoth>Clapperoth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#ff0000>(12/27/02 10:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=435.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 50 BS is this mad?</span><hr size=1> Yes, this would make you less effective in RvR and end game PvE friend.  Speccing Battlesongs past 46 gives you very little or no benefits.  Our 50 spec Song is barely more effective than the previous Song of Rest, which is itself more or less useless.  And you will do very little additional damage from having more Battlesongs spec. <p>Clapperoth Liefarg&lt;BR&gt;<br>
